description: Introducing Unit 507 at The Blake, a vibrant new construction from 2022, offering a contemporary living experience in one of South Boston’s most sought-after locations. This unit is designed with style and function in mind, featuring elegant finishes such as quartz countertops, light oak hardwood floors, a grey-tiled backsplash, and two-tone cabinetry, creating a striking first impression. The spacious dining and living areas are perfect for entertaining, with a private balcony that provides stunning city views. The primary bedroom offers a spacious closet and a luxurious en-suite bath, complete with a rainfall shower and double vanity. The generously sized second bedroom, which could easily serve as an office or guest room, is conveniently located next to a full bath. Residents of The Blake also enjoy exceptional amenities, a large complimentary gym, and an expansive rooftop deck with beautiful city views and a gas grill. Unit also comes with parking.
